                <listBibl><bibl>AE 1903, 0179.</bibl><bibl>AE 1903, 0180.</bibl><bibl>IMS 4, 129; Foto.</bibl><bibl>M.M. Vassits, RA 1903, 26-28; fig. 20. - AE 1903.</bibl><bibl>CIL 03, 14595, 1.</bibl><bibl/></listBibl>
            </div>
